    <title>Welcome</title>
</head>

<body style=" background-color: black; width: 100%; height: 100vh; overflow-x: hidden;">
    <div class="email" style="display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;">
        <div class="main" style="width: 100%; background-color: white; display: flexbox; align-items: center;">
            <div style="align-items: center;">

                <div class="head" style="
                display: flexbox;
                align-items: center;
                justify-content: center;
                background-color: #5C53FF;
                text-align: center;
                color: white;
                padding: 1.5rem 0;"
              >
                  <div style="align-items: center;">
                      <h4 style="font-size: 1.2rem; font-weight: 700;">Air Separation</h4>
                      <div class="middle" style="margin-top: 3rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;">
                          <span style="
                            background-color: #FFA046;
                            padding: 0.65rem;
                            border-radius: 20px;
                            text-transform: uppercase;
                            font-weight: 600;
                            font-size: 0.7rem;"
                          >Invitation to join ASNL TEAM</span>
                      </div>

                      <h1 style="font-size: 2.5rem;
                      font-weight: 700;
                      font-weight: 700;">Gas Confirmation</h1>
                  </div>
              </div>
              <div class="body" style="padding: 1.5rem 4rem;
                font-family: Verdana, Geneva, Tahoma, sans-serif;
                font-size: 16px;
                letter-spacing: 0.05em;
                text-align: left;
                line-height: 1.625;
                color: #2f2d2d;"
              >
                  <p>Hi</p>

                  <p> You have been added to the ASNL {{team}} group as the {{role}} in {{branch}} branch.
                    Use this Email: <b>{{email}}</b> and Password:<b>{{password}}</b> to login. Please click on the button bellow to login and
                    change your password </p>
                      <p>Regards... ASNL team</p>
                  <div class="action" style="width: 100%;display: flex;align-items: center; justify-content: center; text-align: center;">
                      <button style="
                        margin: 25px 0;
                        background-color: #5C53FF;
                        color: white;
                        width: 30%;
                        padding: 1rem;
                        border-radius: 10px;
                        text-transform: uppercase;
                        font-weight: 600;
                        font-size: 1rem;
                        text-align: center;
                        "
                      >
                        <a style="color: white;" href={{link}}>Login</a>
                      </button>
                  </div>

                  <p class="footnote" style="
                    font-size: 0.6rem;
                    font-size: 0.7rem;
                    line-height: 1.2;
                    letter-spacing: 0.05rem;
                    text-align: left;--tw-text-opacity: 1;
                    color: rgba(156, 163, 175, var(--tw-text-opacity));"
                  >
                      <p> This email was sent to you as a registered member of ASNL. Use of the service and website is
                          subject to our <a href="">Terms of Service</a> and <a href="">Privacy Policy</a></p>
                      <p class="middle" style="
                        margin-top: 3rem;
                        margin-bottom: 1rem;
                        text-align:center;"
                      >© 2021 ASNL. All rights reserved</p>
                  </p>

              </div>

            </div>

        </div>

    </div>


</body>

